videoSnippet.title: You're Not Going Anywhere || Navara vs Duda || Prague Chess Festival (2020)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

David Navara vs Jan Krzysztof Duda
Prague Chess Festival - Masters
12.2.2020.
Sicilian, Najdorf, Adams attack (B90)

Qf3 Bg5 18. h4 Qe3+ 19. Qxe3 Bxe3 20. Ke2 Ba7 21. Rad1 Bd7 22. Kf3 Ke7 23. Rh2 Rhg8 24. Bh3 Ba4 25. Rhd2 Rac8 26. Bf1 Rg6 27. Nh5 Bd4 28. Bd3 Rcg8 29. Rg2 f5 30. exf5 Bc6+ 31. Ke2 exf5 32.
